1
00:00:00,040 --> 00:00:10,040
[English subtitles are available.]


2
00:02:19,960 --> 00:02:22,520
[Episode 5]


3
00:02:35,320 --> 00:02:36,560
Mo's Carefree Weed?


4
00:02:36,640 --> 00:02:37,680
A weed?


5
00:02:39,480 --> 00:02:41,000
This is an invaluable treasure.


6
00:02:41,360 --> 00:02:42,600
Only one weed grows in a century.


7
00:02:42,760 --> 00:02:44,160
It's worth thousands, Master.


8
00:02:44,240 --> 00:02:45,840
I've surely suffered a huge loss.


9
00:02:50,960 --> 00:02:51,960
What did you just say?


10
00:02:52,520 --> 00:02:53,480
This thing...


11
00:02:54,600 --> 00:02:55,640
is worth thousands?


12
00:02:58,440 --> 00:02:59,800
I'm going to be rich this time.


13
00:03:04,760 --> 00:03:06,000
[Carefree Weed?]


14
00:03:06,680 --> 00:03:07,640
[The Mo family?]


15
00:03:09,320 --> 00:03:10,240
[Mo Lin?]


16
00:03:11,320 --> 00:03:12,160
Master.


17
00:03:12,400 --> 00:03:13,520
Since the mistake has been made,


18
00:03:13,760 --> 00:03:14,960
he should make up for it.


19
00:03:15,520 --> 00:03:16,400
I'll go...


20
00:03:17,400 --> 00:03:19,640
I'll go and get Mo Lin
to make up for his mistake.


21
00:03:20,200 --> 00:03:21,120
It's just that...


22
00:03:21,360 --> 00:03:23,560
strangers aren't allowed
into the hall of Zhaifeng Institute.


23
00:03:23,640 --> 00:03:25,240
I'm not done yet.


24
00:03:26,960 --> 00:03:27,960
In the next few days,


25
00:03:28,040 --> 00:03:29,800
I have to go to Chan State
to borrow a martial arts tower.


26
00:03:29,960 --> 00:03:31,360
Zhaifeng Institute will be in your care.


27
00:03:31,640 --> 00:03:33,200
As long as there's no trouble,


28
00:03:33,280 --> 00:03:34,760
I'll pretend as if nothing has happened.


29
00:03:36,160 --> 00:03:37,280
Thank you, Master.


30
00:03:41,520 --> 00:03:42,840
[Mo's Carefree Weed?]


31
00:04:05,640 --> 00:04:06,560
Kid.


32
00:04:06,800 --> 00:04:07,640
This...


33
00:04:08,040 --> 00:04:09,960
I have a lot of gadgets in my bag.


34
00:04:10,440 --> 00:04:12,160
I'll exchange one for your bread. Okay?


35
00:04:14,720 --> 00:04:15,600
You don't believe me?


36
00:04:15,680 --> 00:04:16,519
I'll show them to you.


37
00:04:18,320 --> 00:04:19,160
Kid.


38
00:04:19,519 --> 00:04:20,440
Come back!


39
00:04:23,560 --> 00:04:25,760
Do you want a nice meal
in Ruyu Restaurant?


40
00:04:27,640 --> 00:04:29,240
It depends on my mood.


41
00:04:40,880 --> 00:04:41,720
This flavor...


42
00:04:41,920 --> 00:04:43,200
I can make do with it.


43
00:04:45,200 --> 00:04:46,400
We'll meet again if possible.


44
00:04:46,640 --> 00:04:47,440
Your last name is Mo.


45
00:04:47,600 --> 00:04:49,400
Have you heard of the Mo family
in Carefree Valley?


46
00:04:52,720 --> 00:04:55,720
The Mo family is renowned
for their knowledge in herbal medicine.


47
00:04:56,080 --> 00:04:58,520
It's said that they can restore
the dying to health.


48
00:04:59,280 --> 00:05:00,400
Centuries ago,


49
00:05:00,720 --> 00:05:03,160
to avoid getting into
the disputes of the martial arts world,


50
00:05:03,240 --> 00:05:04,960
the entire Mo clan withdrew
into Carefree Valley.


51
00:05:05,720 --> 00:05:07,240
The Mo family of Carefree Valley?


52
00:05:07,840 --> 00:05:09,120
I don't know what you're saying.


53
00:05:09,320 --> 00:05:11,760
The chief of Carefree Valley,
Mo Buliu has a son.


54
00:05:11,880 --> 00:05:13,400
He is about your age.


55
00:05:13,920 --> 00:05:16,480
The Mo family has a unique bloodline.


56
00:05:16,760 --> 00:05:19,400
They are born
without any soul of Strength.


57
00:05:20,040 --> 00:05:20,920
Mr. Mo...


58
00:05:21,360 --> 00:05:23,320
does the chief know that
you're wandering out here?


59
00:05:24,320 --> 00:05:25,120
That's enough.


60
00:05:25,360 --> 00:05:26,360
Hats off to you.


61
00:05:26,840 --> 00:05:28,080
I'm from Carefree Valley. So?


62
00:05:28,200 --> 00:05:29,360
Mo Buliu is my father.


63
00:05:30,400 --> 00:05:32,200
A physician without the soul of Strength.


64
00:05:32,320 --> 00:05:33,320
You want to be an assassin?


65
00:05:33,400 --> 00:05:35,960
Who said I can't have a dream
because I don't have the soul of Strength?


66
00:05:36,960 --> 00:05:38,560
I don't want to be like my father.


67
00:05:38,760 --> 00:05:40,120
All they do is hide in the valley


68
00:05:40,200 --> 00:05:41,400
and serve as physicians for life.


69
00:05:41,640 --> 00:05:42,440
One day,


70
00:05:42,640 --> 00:05:44,680
I'll be sure to wipe out
all the villains in the world


71
00:05:44,800 --> 00:05:46,400
and become the best assassin.


72
00:05:47,120 --> 00:05:48,680
Since you have such an ambition,


73
00:05:48,800 --> 00:05:50,520
you must be righteous at heart.


74
00:05:50,640 --> 00:05:51,560
Of course.


75
00:05:51,640 --> 00:05:52,880
That's good.


76
00:05:53,120 --> 00:05:55,159
The physicians of Carefree Valley
are extremely skilled.


77
00:05:55,240 --> 00:05:56,760
Now that Lu Ping is severely injured,


78
00:05:56,920 --> 00:05:58,960
come with me to Zhaifeng Institute
to attend to his wounds.


79
00:06:00,200 --> 00:06:01,040
Lu Ping?


80
00:06:01,240 --> 00:06:02,760
Even if I starve
for three days and nights,


81
00:06:02,840 --> 00:06:04,920
I won't get involved with that jinx.


82
00:06:05,200 --> 00:06:06,000
I'm off.


83
00:06:15,840 --> 00:06:16,640
Su Tang.


84
00:06:17,040 --> 00:06:18,640
Judging by your character,


85
00:06:18,760 --> 00:06:20,440
you won't leave Lu Ping in the lurch.


86
00:06:20,600 --> 00:06:21,560
Seeing what you just did,


87
00:06:21,760 --> 00:06:22,680
I was right after all.


88
00:06:22,840 --> 00:06:24,320
Lu Ping didn't save you for nothing.


89
00:06:24,440 --> 00:06:26,320
Aren't you afraid
that I have an ulterior motive?


90
00:06:26,640 --> 00:06:29,000
Lu Ping has always tackled
his obstacles alone.


91
00:06:29,480 --> 00:06:32,120
Apart from me, hardly anyone else
had offered him any help.


92
00:06:32,320 --> 00:06:33,720
What's the harm in trusting you once?


93
00:06:34,960 --> 00:06:36,640
If this fellow can really save Lu Ping,


94
00:06:36,760 --> 00:06:38,480
-I'll take him back by force.
-I'm not an object.


95
00:06:38,560 --> 00:06:39,800
Don't use me to obtain favors.


96
00:06:47,320 --> 00:06:48,520
Your soul of Strength...


97
00:06:48,840 --> 00:06:50,360
Are you already close to mastering it?


98
00:06:50,440 --> 00:06:52,000
Why are you so bossy?


99
00:06:53,480 --> 00:06:54,320
Stop it!


100
00:06:54,400 --> 00:06:55,360
If you beat me senseless,


101
00:06:55,440 --> 00:06:56,680
no one can save your godbrother.


102
00:06:56,800 --> 00:06:58,000
So you've agreed to save him?


103
00:07:02,080 --> 00:07:04,520
I don't have the soul of Strength.


104
00:07:04,880 --> 00:07:05,680
But...


105
00:07:06,160 --> 00:07:07,640
If I get to be attended


106
00:07:07,720 --> 00:07:09,080
by a disciple of the soul of Strength,


107
00:07:09,760 --> 00:07:10,840
that seems quite nice as well.


108
00:07:11,080 --> 00:07:11,960
Why don't you...


109
00:07:12,160 --> 00:07:13,000
be my disciple?


110
00:07:14,080 --> 00:07:15,800
Make a living with me
in the martial arts world.


111
00:07:15,920 --> 00:07:17,240
As for saving him,


112
00:07:18,000 --> 00:07:19,160
I can give it some thought.


113
00:07:20,360 --> 00:07:21,360
You want me


114
00:07:21,640 --> 00:07:22,640
to leave with you?


115
00:07:23,280 --> 00:07:24,200
That's right.


116
00:07:28,240 --> 00:07:29,760
It's awesome to be an assassin.


117
00:07:29,880 --> 00:07:31,000
A lot of people came begging me,


118
00:07:31,080 --> 00:07:32,440
but I turned them down.


119
00:07:32,520 --> 00:07:33,600
Just reconsider it.


120
00:07:38,720 --> 00:07:40,320
Zhao Xifan said


121
00:07:40,480 --> 00:07:42,360
that I'm the only one
who can save your godbrother.


122
00:07:42,480 --> 00:07:43,520
You either become my disciple


123
00:07:43,840 --> 00:07:46,200
or you are on your own.


124
00:07:47,240 --> 00:07:48,280
You really won't save him?


125
00:07:48,520 --> 00:07:50,159
I won't save him
even if you grab me by force.


126
00:07:50,600 --> 00:07:51,440
Fine.


127
00:07:51,520 --> 00:07:53,120
Zhaifeng Institute doesn't force anyone.


128
00:07:53,560 --> 00:07:54,440
Let's go, Su Tang.


129
00:07:54,600 --> 00:07:55,760
We'll find someone better.


130
00:08:00,800 --> 00:08:01,760
Hey.


131
00:08:02,320 --> 00:08:03,800
You're leaving?


132
00:08:04,560 --> 00:08:05,760
Give it some thought!


133
00:08:17,040 --> 00:08:19,160
I've really spent a lot of money
on this trip


134
00:08:19,600 --> 00:08:22,360
to borrow the martial arts tower.


135
00:08:22,440 --> 00:08:23,480
What do you think?


136
00:08:26,280 --> 00:08:27,560
I'm talking to you.


137
00:08:28,200 --> 00:08:29,600
What are you doing?


138
00:08:35,280 --> 00:08:36,159
Nice to meet you.


139
00:08:37,080 --> 00:08:38,799
Please inform your chief


140
00:08:40,840 --> 00:08:42,280
that Guo Youdao of Zhaifeng Institute


141
00:08:42,360 --> 00:08:43,600
would like to see him.


142
00:08:53,160 --> 00:08:54,040
Good tea.


143
00:08:55,120 --> 00:08:55,960
Master Guo.


144
00:08:56,440 --> 00:08:58,080
I can't be bothered
to beat around the bush.


145
00:08:58,440 --> 00:09:01,000
In regard to borrowing
the martial arts tower...


146
00:09:01,800 --> 00:09:02,600
You can't.


147
00:09:04,160 --> 00:09:05,160
Sir.


148
00:09:05,320 --> 00:09:07,080
How can you say that?


149
00:09:07,240 --> 00:09:10,280
We share years of friendship
between our martial arts academies.


150
00:09:11,520 --> 00:09:12,840
Don't shoot your mouth off.


151
00:09:13,040 --> 00:09:13,880
Right.


152
00:09:14,600 --> 00:09:15,440
First of all,


153
00:09:15,840 --> 00:09:17,000
here in Shuo,


154
00:09:17,080 --> 00:09:18,240
apart from the Tianzhao Academy


155
00:09:18,320 --> 00:09:19,680
founded by the aristocrats in Kaifeng,


156
00:09:20,240 --> 00:09:22,520
the others are run by officials.


157
00:09:23,480 --> 00:09:24,760
Mine is the only one


158
00:09:24,840 --> 00:09:26,320
in the city of Chan State.


159
00:09:27,160 --> 00:09:30,000
Zhaifeng Institute relies solely on you


160
00:09:30,080 --> 00:09:31,760
to get by until this day.


161
00:09:31,840 --> 00:09:33,400
It can't be called a martial arts academy.


162
00:09:35,120 --> 00:09:36,160
Secondly,


163
00:09:36,640 --> 00:09:39,000
the martial arts tower was sponsored
by the Wei family.


164
00:09:39,400 --> 00:09:41,400
It's built for the State Exam.


165
00:09:42,480 --> 00:09:44,320
Besides, this year's exam


166
00:09:44,400 --> 00:09:45,920
will affect the Soul Combat Convention.


167
00:09:46,360 --> 00:09:48,120
If the disciples of my academy


168
00:09:48,280 --> 00:09:49,600
get to win a place


169
00:09:49,680 --> 00:09:50,760
at the Soul Combat Convention,


170
00:09:50,920 --> 00:09:54,440
they will serve the state as officials.


171
00:09:55,760 --> 00:09:57,840
Zhaifeng Institute
doesn't even pay a single tael


172
00:09:58,000 --> 00:10:00,640
and yet you want to borrow
the tower for the exam.


173
00:10:01,400 --> 00:10:03,800
Master Guo, that's trying
to curry favors empty-handed.


174
00:10:05,120 --> 00:10:08,040
Isn't that a wishful thinking?


175
00:10:10,920 --> 00:10:12,840
The disciples of Zhaifeng Institute


176
00:10:12,920 --> 00:10:15,440
might be a bit poor,


177
00:10:15,520 --> 00:10:16,320
but...


178
00:10:16,480 --> 00:10:18,120
they also have the wish
to serve the country.


179
00:10:18,280 --> 00:10:19,880
Just lend it to me this time.


180
00:10:20,400 --> 00:10:21,360
As for the fees,


181
00:10:21,560 --> 00:10:22,680
can you...


182
00:10:23,120 --> 00:10:24,840
-put it on the tab first?
-"Put it on the tab"?


183
00:10:25,280 --> 00:10:27,000
Hang on, do you think
this is some charity shop?


184
00:10:28,160 --> 00:10:29,360
I'll be honest with you.


185
00:10:29,480 --> 00:10:31,880
This year's outcome will affect
the future of my disciples.


186
00:10:32,360 --> 00:10:33,680
No one will take pity on you.


187
00:10:35,040 --> 00:10:36,000
See the guest out.


188
00:10:36,280 --> 00:10:37,120
Sir!


189
00:10:37,200 --> 00:10:38,040
Hold on.


190
00:10:38,120 --> 00:10:39,160
Wait...


191
00:10:40,040 --> 00:10:40,840
Sir.


192
00:10:40,920 --> 00:10:42,880
-We're old friends...
-Hold on.


193
00:10:45,520 --> 00:10:46,600
Mr. Wei.


194
00:10:46,960 --> 00:10:48,400
See, I've told you.


195
00:10:48,560 --> 00:10:49,640
It's such a hot day.


196
00:10:49,840 --> 00:10:51,040
If you're tired,


197
00:10:51,240 --> 00:10:53,040
you don't have to come here
to practice every day.


198
00:10:53,120 --> 00:10:53,920
Master.


199
00:10:54,120 --> 00:10:56,160
I'm after all the top disciple
of Chan State's martial arts academy.


200
00:10:56,240 --> 00:10:57,080
That's true.


201
00:10:57,160 --> 00:10:58,920
I should serve as a role model
for my peers, right?


202
00:10:59,040 --> 00:11:00,120
How can I neglect my training?


203
00:11:00,200 --> 00:11:01,040
You're right.


204
00:11:03,360 --> 00:11:05,000
Isn't this Master Guo
of Zhaifeng Institute?


205
00:11:06,280 --> 00:11:07,200
Isn't this...


206
00:11:07,280 --> 00:11:08,240
Mr. Wei?


207
00:11:08,440 --> 00:11:09,840
I've long heard that Mr. Wei


208
00:11:09,920 --> 00:11:12,920
is the top disciple here
in Chan State's academy.


209
00:11:13,080 --> 00:11:14,280
Having seen you today,


210
00:11:14,360 --> 00:11:15,880
you truly are charming.


211
00:11:16,520 --> 00:11:18,200
You're the best of the best.


212
00:11:18,560 --> 00:11:19,440
Master.


213
00:11:19,640 --> 00:11:22,640
Our academy is close
to Zhaifeng Institute.


214
00:11:22,760 --> 00:11:24,040
We've always been friendly.


215
00:11:24,640 --> 00:11:25,920
Isn't it just a martial arts tower?


216
00:11:26,000 --> 00:11:26,960
What's the harm in lending it to them?


217
00:11:27,040 --> 00:11:27,840
Exactly.


218
00:11:27,920 --> 00:11:28,960
Disciples of both academies


219
00:11:29,040 --> 00:11:30,600
can learn from each other
in the same tower.


220
00:11:30,680 --> 00:11:31,520
Good!


221
00:11:33,360 --> 00:11:34,880
Since Mr. Wei said so,


222
00:11:35,000 --> 00:11:36,120
I can surely lend it to you.


223
00:11:36,680 --> 00:11:38,320
That's great.


224
00:11:38,800 --> 00:11:39,920
Thank you, sir.


225
00:11:40,080 --> 00:11:41,240
Thank you, Mr. Wei.


226
00:11:41,320 --> 00:11:42,120
All right.


227
00:11:43,360 --> 00:11:44,320
Let go of me!


228
00:11:45,280 --> 00:11:46,240
What are you doing?


229
00:11:50,560 --> 00:11:51,560
Let go of me!


230
00:11:52,880 --> 00:11:54,200
-Let go of me!
-I say, the both of you


231
00:11:54,360 --> 00:11:56,120
simply brought my patient here by force?


232
00:11:56,720 --> 00:11:58,080
If this adds to his injuries,


233
00:11:58,280 --> 00:11:59,080
what am I to do?


234
00:11:59,200 --> 00:12:01,760
That fellow's meridians
must have been damaged by Situ Luo.


235
00:12:01,880 --> 00:12:03,120
His souls power are obstructed.


236
00:12:03,400 --> 00:12:05,040
I'll need silver needles
to get the flow going.


237
00:12:06,920 --> 00:12:08,480
You really know how to treat it?


238
00:12:09,040 --> 00:12:10,880
It's only for my disciple's sake


239
00:12:10,960 --> 00:12:12,120
that I'm helping him.


240
00:12:12,960 --> 00:12:13,760
However,


241
00:12:13,920 --> 00:12:15,840
I've made two bad bargains already.


242
00:12:15,920 --> 00:12:16,840
This time,


243
00:12:16,920 --> 00:12:18,280
I should at least get a good prospect?


244
00:12:18,520 --> 00:12:19,520
As long as you save Lu Ping,


245
00:12:19,680 --> 00:12:20,800
I'll do as you wish.


246
00:12:21,760 --> 00:12:22,680
Wait and see.


247
00:12:22,800 --> 00:12:23,600
One day,


248
00:12:23,680 --> 00:12:26,360
you'll willingly be my disciple.


249
00:12:31,240 --> 00:12:32,240
Zhao Xifan.


250
00:12:32,560 --> 00:12:34,560
Don't go meddling in my business.


251
00:12:35,040 --> 00:12:37,200
You were injured
because of Zhaifeng Institute.


252
00:12:37,480 --> 00:12:38,800
I can't sit and do nothing about it.


253
00:12:39,080 --> 00:12:40,200
Once you've recovered,


254
00:12:40,280 --> 00:12:41,160
our debts are cleared.


255
00:12:41,280 --> 00:12:43,280
Do what you will. I won't stop you.


256
00:12:48,080 --> 00:12:49,000
Lu Ping.


257
00:12:49,080 --> 00:12:50,400
Just give it a try.


258
00:12:50,760 --> 00:12:52,760
The Mo family of Carefree Valley
are known for their medical expertise.


259
00:12:52,920 --> 00:12:54,480
He can surely cure you.


260
00:13:09,120 --> 00:13:09,960
This is extraordinary...


261
00:13:10,360 --> 00:13:11,520
Absolutely extraordinary.


262
00:13:11,800 --> 00:13:13,720
This is the first time
I've ever seen such a pulse.


263
00:13:13,840 --> 00:13:14,720
What kind of pulse?


264
00:13:15,480 --> 00:13:17,280
"Eight extraordinary meridians
induced six souls."


265
00:13:17,520 --> 00:13:20,160
Most people start training
in martial arts by learning one soul.


266
00:13:20,640 --> 00:13:21,840
After training for decades,


267
